Package com.example.quacks_app

Class Facility

java.lang.Object
com.example.quacks_app.RepoModel
com.example.quacks_app.Facility
All Implemented Interfaces:
Listable, Serializable
public class Facility extends RepoModel implements Serializable, Listable
Represents a facility with its geographical location, contact information, and associated events. Implements Serializable for object serialization and Listable for UI representation.
